&lt;p&gt;Here are the notes from the demo (taken from &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yBW91iNOGSvqM8JLeFH6IhXt_98I-GKkPlXYDb4M3EY/edit"&gt;this&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Python&amp;nbsp;Anywhere&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://roycesite.com/george/media/DeployDjangoPA/DeployDjangoPA.html"&gt;Video Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1hbzr7bqp3ylmqDSgM7adEqi06ttSVsDLsPuwas9QLQ0/edit"&gt;Written&amp;nbsp;Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Heroku&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://roycesite.com/george/media/deploy2herokuv2/deploy2herokuv2.html"&gt;Video Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Eocf7QGXIMoFY4_NwaeG_vmC0kxmGWFw/view"&gt;Written Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;
